{"tid":1742104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港金總將於11月23日召開特別會員大會","createTime":"2019-11-20T15:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T10:43:40.000Z","uid":194325,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a7920072cc893d2bda8cf7835983ba7626e178fc","tid":1742104,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:33:29.000Z","msg":"最新消息<br />\n<br />\n香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於2019年11月23日（星期六）下午5時正舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。會議地點尚有待確定，唯盡量安排於九龍或港島區一帶。最新消息將2019年11月22日（星期五）前盡快公佈。<br />\n<br />\n有意者請從Facebook 或Telegram與工會成員聯絡，以獲得地點詳情。並帶同身份證明文件連同工作證明(例如工作證、公司名片等)以作身份核對及認證之用。<br />\n<br />\n我們歡迎同路人前來分享交流。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=a66d9703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=de64bc74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=c1aa189b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=c26f3d95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#招收會員<br />\n#特別會員大會"},{"pid":"16eeab2b143cd602b90bf4debcb9e0c19b9139b9","tid":1742104,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:34:30.000Z","ms